{"tid":1462330,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"［認真檢討近月行動方向］ 五大訴求！","createTime":"2019-08-13T10:23:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T10:36:46.000Z","uid":219163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"34cb852fa41b8d633a24a03ccf9f2392db810eb3","tid":1462330,"uid":219163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T10:23:14.000Z","msg":"辛苦機場巴打 不割席 不分化<br />\n<br />\n呢場運動輸既代價好大 係7百萬人既命運 <br />\n求你地一定要仔細諗諗 唔好比一時怒氣令到自己失去方向！ <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n1. 獨立調查既成效未必好似我地想像中咁有效<br />\n2. 我地幾仇警都好，點起底都好，真正清算方法只有推反現有政制，實行雙普選 &mdash;&gt; 先真正可以清算狗警！</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n我地絕對要檢討我地而家既方向 係要真正而長遠 <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">千萬唔好比狗警帶到風向 佢地最想見到我地無目標！無計劃！分化！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n篇文有啲長 但請求你地睇一睇！<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/w0PqtQg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fw0PqtQg.jpg&h=9e174e38&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YrkAQ3B.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYrkAQ3B.jpg&h=629f9312&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tjTe6BX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtjTe6BX.jpg&h=9f655e7a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OVKua3D.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOVKua3D.jpg&h=a136ad72&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ipAEygZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FipAEygZ.jpg&h=37a05b36&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9XiVQ3E.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9XiVQ3E.jpg&h=06507726&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3a9d3cf765b401889c9c4a505c471c5f7becf53b","tid":1462330,"uid":219163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T10:23:30.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a675913ab7e01678a6f67c95315c721af12d8bec","ti